---

<div class="container">
  <p class="top-text">The Simplest and the Cheapest way to</p>
  <h1>Build your restaurant menu app</h1>
  <p class="bottom-text">
    Want to build your own restaurant app?. we create customizable app, perfect
    for your restaurant in the most affordable way. stay with us to know more
  </p>
  <div class="flex-center bottom-div">
    <button class="flex-center"
      >DOWNLOAD
      <img class="down-icon" src="./home/download_icon.svg" />
    </button>
    <img class="bottom-img" src="./home/bottom-side-icon.svg" />
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .flex-center {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .top-text {
    color: var(--accent-mid);
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }
  h1 {
    width: 12ch;
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-block: 0.5rem;
  }
  .bottom-text {
    color: #7d7d7d;
    max-width: 40ch;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }
  .bottom-div {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  button {
    background-color: var(--accent);
    border: none;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
  }
  .down-icon {
    transform: translateX(0.3em);
    width: 1.3em;
  }
  .bottom-img {
    width: 11rem;
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }

  @media only screen and (orientation: portrait) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.3rem;
    }
    .container {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-block: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
